{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb7504f963","title":"关于对苏共纲领的意见《备忘录》稿的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1376030922","index":1,"year":1963,"month":4,"day":20,"articleId":"cb7504f963"},{"id":"5abd20163d","index":0,"year":1963,"month":4,"day":9,"articleId":"cb7504f963"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"5d0d481c35","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个《备忘录》初稿说，苏共领导人把苏共二十二大纲领当成国际共产党人的共同纲领，中共中央认为有必要在举行两党会谈的时候，对苏共纲领提出自己的意见。备忘录就下列问题闸述了意见：（一）关于社会主义的最终胜利；（二）关于无产阶级专政的历史使命；（三）关于所谓“全民党”；（四）关于所谓“物质刺激”；（五）关于所谓“新型的国际分工”；（六）关于所谓“一切为了人”和“人道主义”。这个备忘录后来没有发出。"},{"id":"996feca55c","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"本篇一是毛泽东在《备忘录》的部分手抄稿上写的批语。本篇二是毛泽东在陈伯达1963年4月13日送阅的《备忘录（初稿）》铅印件上写的批语。"},{"id":"9e3902a23d","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"伯达，即陈伯达，当时任中共中央政治局候补委员、中央政治研究室主任、毛泽东的秘书。"}],"contents":[{"id":"40926626ce","type":"title","text":"关于对苏共纲领的意见《备忘录》稿的批语？","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963"},{"id":"5d0d481c35","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963"},{"id":"996feca55c","type":"paragraph","text":"这些都已看过，写得很好。未完部分，请续寄来。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963"},{"id":"9e3902a23d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"cb7504f963"},{"id":"73d28d8d28","type":"paragraph","text":"四月九日上午二时已阅一遍。","ind